# Dynamic Footer Versioning and Workflow

Add a version number to the frontend footer that updates automatically before each deployment/push. The version will follow a `major.minor.patch` format (v2 branch) and be managed via a JSON file and a custom increment script.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> The versioning script will increment the **patch** version (last digit) by default. You can specify a **minor** (middle digit) increment via a flag in the workflow script.
> The version will be displayed in the footer with a font size of 4px as requested.

## Proposed Changes

### Version Management
#### [NEW] [version.json](file:///mnt/WebliesNew/test-and-notes-upgrading/version.json)
Create a `version.json` file in the root to store the current version state.
```json
{
    "major": 2,
    "minor": 0,
    "patch": 0
}
```

#### [MODIFY] [app.php](file:///mnt/WebliesNew/test-and-notes-upgrading/config/app.php)
Expose the version to the application by reading it from `version.json`.
```php
'version' => json_decode(file_get_contents(base_path('version.json')), true),
```

### Scripting & Automation
#### [NEW] [increment-version.php](file:///mnt/WebliesNew/test-and-notes-upgrading/.agent/scripts/increment-version.php)
A PHP script to handle version increments (middle or last constraint).

#### [NEW] [push.md](file:///mnt/WebliesNew/test-and-notes-upgrading/.agent/workflows/push.md)
A new workflow to automate the update process:
1. Increment version.
2. Run `npm run build`.
3. Run `vendor/bin/pint --dirty`.
4. Inform user that the project is ready for `git push`.

### Frontend
#### [MODIFY] [footer.blade.php](file:///mnt/WebliesNew/test-and-notes-upgrading/resources/views/livewire/frontend/components/footer.blade.php)
Add the version number to the bottom of the footer with the requested styling (4px).

## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- Run the `increment-version.php` script and verify `version.json` update.
- Run the `push` workflow steps manually to ensure they complete without errors.

### Manual Verification
- Check the footer in the browser to ensure the version is visible and correctly styled at 4px.
